    <abstract>
      <t>This document describes the Large BGP Community attribute, an extension to BGP (RFC 4271). This attribute provides a mechanism to signal opaque information within separate namespaces to aid in routing management. The attribute is suitable for use in 4-byte ASNs (RFC 6793).</t>
